@startuml
actor Client
participant CommentsController
participant User
participant Comment

Client -> CommentsController: GET request to /comments with x-auth-token header
note right: Client requests all comments

CommentsController -> User: assertAuth(token, secret)
note right: Validate authentication token

alt Token is valid
    CommentsController -> Comment: fetch_all()
    note right: Retrieve all comments from database
    Comment --> CommentsController: List<Comment>
    CommentsController --> Client: Return comment list as JSON response
    note right: Send comments to client
else Token validation fails
    User --> CommentsController: Authentication error
    note right: Token validation failure
    CommentsController --> Client: Return authentication error
    note right: Authentication failure response (HTTP 401)
end
@enduml